data.description: Spotless...that will be your first impression upon entering the front door. The large kitchen overlooking the comfortable living room with corner fireplace is an open concept and one of the larger homes in the neighborhood,yet remains warm and cozy. Truly designed for entertaining. No space is wasted here with 4 bedrooms and 2 baths. Sit outside under the covered patio and enjoy the privacy of no back neighbors and plenty of yard space. Snatch up this jewel before it''s too late to make it yours!
